{"tid":1889181,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】確診警員妻子外母現病徵","createTime":"2020-02-20T14:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:14:47.000Z","uid":66271,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2d92e973504a5f233a4993c484504878ba92f8","tid":1889181,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/S8Y0HLpaGAUTpDJ2N_yBOo2pw8Y=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7BKJ7ZHMHLGUEXSWSL6KGJTK6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FS8Y0HLpaGAUTpDJ2N_yBOo2pw8Y%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7BKJ7ZHMHLGUEXSWSL6KGJTK6M.jpg&h=84c0932a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港晚上再新增一宗初步確診個案，患者為一名48歲軍裝警員。據悉，該名警員前日（18日）發燒，他近日到觀塘普通科門診求診後，再自行留唾液送交測試，樣本測試初步呈陽性反應。聯合醫院通知他後，由救護車將他送聯合醫院隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，患者居於油美苑潤美閣紀律部隊宿舍，駐守北角警署軍裝巡邏第4小隊。他2月18日出席了一個60人的退休宴會，地點在西環明星酒家，同日就發燒。有公院醫護透露，該名警員在觀塘普通科門診留唾液檢測初步呈陽性，其妻子及外母亦有病徵，已將樣本一併送醫院再檢驗。而西環明星酒家於昨日起突然停業，屬同一集團的北角明星酒家於日前亦突然停業，該處早前為康美樓感染群組聚餐地點。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當日出席宴會的人士大部份駐守西區警署，警方正追蹤有關人士。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局由本月19日起擴大新型冠狀病毒檢測範圍，為症狀輕微的急症室及普通科門診病人進行檢測，由病人自行留唾液再交回急症室或門診進行測試。今次是首次門診化驗而確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警員初步確診時序<br />\n<br />\n2月18日 到西環明星酒家出席60人聚會<br />\n2月19日 請病假到觀塘普通科門診求診<br />\n2月20日 請病假，將自行留唾液樣本送交測試<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200220/VWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ/?fbclid=IwAR1Aszl3lDhITGkaCy02pkiPdoJk9yWs_kJiFPpja3JLmUpz2MbYvtsYni4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2FVWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Aszl3lDhITGkaCy02pkiPdoJk9yWs_kJiFPpja3JLmUpz2MbYvtsYni4&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=54f61c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2FVWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Aszl3lDhITGkaCy02pkiPdoJk9yWs_kJiFPpja3JLmUpz2MbYvtsYni4&h=85c64dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200220/VWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ/?fbclid=IwAR1Aszl3lDhITGkaCy02pkiPdoJk9yWs_kJiFPpja3JLmUpz2MbYvtsYni4</a>"},{"pid":"17f7eecd9ba1707532e301751747937bfb62c971","tid":1889181,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AxSr31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AxSr31.jpg&h=09cc458a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba5d1da9410104016e6eaadff5327d735a3feafe","tid":1889181,"uid":224561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMx3yJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMx3yJf.png&h=6237dd6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50eb6c5b7a14778a48e04574e87580508ca66884","tid":1889181,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb99f1b79b39cd5e79a7a8ebdf040d4c93f12871","tid":1889181,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b5437a7798ecff238e47515855024fb57c7f74","tid":1889181,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"唔係冇仔冇女咁撚慘呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97632c9e63e92ee77808fd513bb07c4c91b7ebbf","tid":1889181,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"黑警 高官 死全家 一齊念力咒撚鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkg